name: Stunten Runnzem
text: Staff seemed nice when I met them. Had like 3 or 4 interviews did a few apps for them had a tour and everything. This was before the convid 19. I have alot of experience in food manufacturing, was a working foremen at a different job. Drove a cross country was in contact with them over a month before moving. Thinking I had a good job for me and my family. Let's just say after finally contact, it felt like they was pulling me around for that whole week. Never got any reason to why they pulled me around. Just saying wasn't happy with my experience with the h r which they didn't even have in house at the time or that's what they told me. Wasted alot of time.
